&lt;p&gt;Chef Pedro Miguel Schiaffino has combined the mastering of Amazonian botanics, Peruvian ingredients and his European training, resulting in a truly unique dining experience that has earned him and &lt;strong&gt;Malabar #20 Latin America&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2015&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;and &lt;strong&gt;#95&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2014&lt;/strong&gt;. Located in Lima&rsquo;s financial district, Malabar is warm and welcoming with lovely art on the walls, but the most beautiful art will be found on the plate. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at &lt;a href=&quot;http://malabar.com.pe/reserva/&quot;&gt;http://malabar.com.pe/reserva/&lt;/a&gt; or contact Malabar by phone at &lt;a href=&quot;Tel: 51 201 440 5200&quot;&gt;+51 1 440 5200&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy &amp;#8211; requires bookings to be canceled at least 24 hours in advance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7 day advance booking recommended for reservations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Amazonian amenity is based on seasonal availability of ingredients and access to Amazonian communities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Same day booking not guaranteed, requests are accepted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

